# Important Docker Commands

Build Image

```bash
docker build -t myimage .
```

List Images

```bash
docker images
```

Run Container

```bash
docker run -d -p 8080:80 myimage
```

Login to Docker Hub

```bash
docker login
```

Tag Image

```bash
docker tag myimage username/myimage:latest
```

Push Image

```bash
docker push username/myimage:latest
```

Pull Image

```bash
docker pull username/myimage:latest
```

